    Common-Name:        - - - - - - - - - - - -
    Common-Name:        - - - - - - - - - - - -
<?sml-space .5>    Options: <Literal>None</Literal>
</Screen>
</Figure>
<?sml-indent>
<?sml-space 2>
<Para>In Mask 2, the <Symbol Role="Variable">operation</Symbol> field will be one of 
the following values, depending on
the operation being performed:
</Para>
<SimpleList Type="Vert">
<Member><Literal>Create Shadows and Shadowing Job</Literal>
</Member>
<Member><Literal>Create Shadowing Job</Literal>
</Member>
<Member><Literal>Remove Shadows and Shadowing Job</Literal>
</Member>
<Member><Literal>Remove Shadowing Job</Literal>
</Member>
<Member><Literal>Update Shadowing Job</Literal>
</Member>
</SimpleList>
<Para>Mask 2 displays the following fields:
</Para>
<VariableList>
<VarListEntry role="linebreak">
<Term><Literal>Country-Name</Literal></Term>
<ListItem>
<?sml-break>
<Para>Enter the <Literal>Country-Name</Literal> part of the DSA's DN.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</VarListEntry>
<VarListEntry role="linebreak">
<Term><Literal>Organization-Name</Literal></Term>
<ListItem>
<?sml-break>
<Para>Enter the <Literal>Organization-Name</Literal> part of the DSA's DN.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</VarListEntry>
<VarListEntry role="linebreak">
<Term><Literal>Org.-Unit-Name</Literal></Term>
<ListItem>
<?sml-break>
<Para>Enter the <Literal>Org.-Unit-Name</Literal> part of the DSA's DN.
<?sml-break><?sml-need 20></Para>
</ListItem>
</VarListEntry>
<VarListEntry role="linebreak">
<Term><Literal>Common-Name</Literal></Term>
<ListItem>
<?sml-break>
<Para>Enter the <Literal>Common-Name</Literal> part of the DSA's DN. 
</Para>
</ListItem>
</VarListEntry>
<VarListEntry role="linebreak">
<Term><Literal>Common-Name</Literal></Term>
<ListItem>
<?sml-break>
<Para>Enter the <Literal>Common-Name</Literal> part of the DSA's DN. (The 
DN of DSA to be selected.)
</Para>
</ListItem>
</VarListEntry>
<VarListEntry>
<Term><Literal>Options</Literal></Term>
<ListItem>
<Para>Select one of the following options by pressing the space bar:
</Para>
<ItemizedList>
<ListItem>
<Para><Literal>None</Literal> (default)
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para><Literal>Changing Name Structure</Literal>
</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
</ListItem>
</VarListEntry>
</VariableList>
<Para>If <Literal>Changing Name Structure</Literal> is selected, 
all structure rules are displayed in
Mask 5.  Only structure rules that represent a DSA can be selected;
that is, structure rules that have the <Literal>Presentation-Address</Literal> attribute.
</Para>
<Para>The only structure in the default schema that represents a DSA is
structure rule 7.
</Para>
<Para>After the selection is made, Mask 2 displays the selected name
structure for entering the DN.  This structure rule is also used
for the next <Literal>Logon to a Specific DSA</Literal> operation.
<IndexTerm Id="OSFGDS.GDSSHA.indx.9" SpanEnd="OSFGDS.GDSSHA.indx.7"><IndexTerm Id="OSFGDS.GDSSHA.indx.10" SpanEnd="OSFGDS.GDSSHA.indx.8"></Para>
