select the structure rule to be processed.
The naming attribute of all structure rules stored in the SRT
are displayed here.  If the SRT contains more than 12 structure rules,
<Literal>&lt;Scroll Up&gt;</Literal> and
<Literal>&lt;Scroll Down&gt;</Literal> can be used to page through the mask.
