<Primary>shadowing jobs</Primary>
<Secondary>selecting operations (mask 13)</Secondary>
</IndexTerm>
<IndexTerm Id="OSFGDS.GDSSHA.indx.21">
<Primary>masks</Primary>
<Secondary>shadow operations (13)</Secondary>
</IndexTerm>
<Para>Mask 13 (Figure 10-5) is used to select the shadow administration operation
to be executed.
</Para>
<Para><!-- .ne 4.0i-->
<?sml-indent 0></Para>
<Figure>
<Title>Mask 13:  Shadow Operations</Title>
