<Member><Literal>SINGLE OBJECT</Literal>
</Member>
<Member><Literal>OBJECT AND ITS SUBORDINATES</Literal>
</Member>
</SimpleList>
<Para>In the <Literal>Job</Literal> field,
<Symbol Role="Variable">job</Symbol> will be one of the following values, depending, 
on the value you selected in Mask 14a:
</Para>
<SimpleList Type="Vert">
<Member><Literal>ACTIVATE UPDATES</Literal>
</Member>
<Member><Literal>MODIFY UPDATE FREQUENCY</Literal>
</Member>
</SimpleList>
<Para>Mask 14c displays the following field:
<?sml-break><?sml-need 20></Para>
<VariableList>
<VarListEntry role="linebreak">
<Term><Literal>Update&ensp;Times</Literal></Term>
<ListItem>
<?sml-break>
<Para>Select one of the following update times by pressing the space bar:
</Para>
<ItemizedList>
<ListItem>
<Para><Literal>EVERY 5 MINUTES</Literal>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para><Literal>EVERY 10 MINUTES</Literal>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para><Literal>EVERY 15 MINUTES</Literal>
</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para><Literal>EVERY 30 MINUTES</Literal>
</Para>
</ListItem>
</ItemizedList>
<Para>The update time in minutes is relative to 0 minutes past the hour. For example,
<Literal>EVERY 10 MINUTES</Literal> means that the updates are done at 0 minutes past
the hour, 10 minutes past the hour, 20 minutes past the hour,
30 minutes past the hour, and so on.
</Para>
</ListItem>
</VarListEntry>
</VariableList>
</Sect3>
