<Symbol Role="Variable">times</Symbol> will be one of the following values, depending
on the value you selected in Mask 14c, 14d, or 14e:
</Para>
<SimpleList Type="Vert">
<Member><Literal>EVERY DAY
</Literal></Member>
<Member>ONCE A WEEK
</Member>
<Member>TWICE A WEEK
</Member>
</SimpleList>
<Para>If <Symbol Role="Variable">times</Symbol> is <Literal>EVERY DAY</Literal>, the <Literal>Day of Week</Literal> fields are
not displayed, and there is only one <Literal>Hours</Literal> field (directly under
<Literal>Update Times</Literal>).
