and one <Literal>Hours</Literal> field.
</Para>
<Para>If <Symbol Role="Variable">times</Symbol> is <Literal>TWICE A WEEK</Literal>, then two <Literal>Day of Week</Literal> fields
and two <Literal>Hours</Literal> fields are displayed (see the preceding mask).
